<lb n="1425b04"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="1425b05"/><head type="no">No. 2898</head>
<lb n="1425b06"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="1"/><jhead><note n="1425036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】大日本續藏經，【甲】光武二年刊本</note>佛說高王觀世音經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="1425b07"/>
<lb n="1425b08"/><div1 type="jing"><p><note n="1425037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（南無）＋觀【甲】</note><app n="1425037"><lem>觀</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">南無觀</rdg></app>世音菩<note n="1425038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">薩＋（三說）細註【甲】</note><app n="1425038"><lem>薩</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">薩<note place="inline">三說</note></rdg></app>。南無佛。南無法。南無僧。佛國
<lb n="1425b09"/>有緣。佛法相因。常樂我淨。有緣佛法。南無摩
<lb n="1425b10"/>訶般若波羅蜜。是大神&CB00057;。南無摩訶般若波
<lb n="1425b11"/>羅蜜。是大明&CB00057;。南無摩訶般若波羅蜜。是無
<lb n="1425b12"/>上&CB00057;南無摩訶般若波羅蜜。是無等等&CB00057;。南
<lb n="1425b13"/>無淨<note n="1425039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">光＋（佛）【甲】</note><app n="1425039"><lem>光</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">光佛</rdg></app>祕<app><lem>密</lem><rdg wit="【大】">蜜</rdg></app>佛。法藏佛。師子吼神足<note n="1425040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">由＝幽【甲】</note><app n="1425040"><lem>由</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">幽</rdg></app>王
<lb n="1425b14"/>佛。佛<note n="1425041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">告＝高【甲】</note><app n="1425041"><lem>告</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">高</rdg></app>須彌登王佛。法護佛。金剛藏師子
<lb n="1425b15"/>游戲佛。寶勝佛。神通佛。藥師琉璃光<note n="1425042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔王〕－【甲】</note><app n="1425042"><lem>王</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>佛。
<lb n="1425b16"/>普光功德山王佛。善住功德寶王佛。過去七
<lb n="1425b17"/>佛。未來<note n="1425043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賢＝現【甲】</note><app n="1425043"><lem>賢</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">現</rdg></app>劫千佛。千五百佛。萬五千佛。五
<lb n="1425b18"/>百花勝佛。百億金剛藏佛。定光佛。六方六佛
<lb n="1425b19"/>名號。東方寶光月殿<note n="1425044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔月〕－【甲】</note><app n="1425044"><lem>月</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>妙尊音王佛。南方樹
<lb n="1425b20"/>根花王佛。西方皂王神通焰花王佛。北方月
<lb n="1425b21"/>殿清淨佛。上方無數精進寶首佛。下方善<note n="1425045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">寂＝積【甲】</note><app n="1425045"><lem>寂</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">積</rdg></app>
<lb n="1425b22"/>月音王佛無量諸佛。多寶佛。釋迦牟尼佛。彌
<lb n="1425b23"/>勒佛。阿&CB00434;佛。<note n="1425046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（阿）＋彌【甲】</note><app n="1425046"><lem>彌</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">阿彌</rdg></app>陀佛。中央一切眾<note n="1425047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">生＝聖【甲】</note><app n="1425047"><lem>生</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">聖</rdg></app>。在佛
<lb n="1425b24"/><note n="1425048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">世＝土【甲】</note><app n="1425048"><lem>世</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">土</rdg></app>界中<note n="1425049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">者＋（梵王帝釋）【甲】</note><app n="1425049"><lem>者</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">者梵王帝釋</rdg></app>。行住於地上。及在虛空中。慈憂
<lb n="1425b25"/>於一切眾生。各令安穩休息。晝夜<note n="1425050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">修持＝受持身【甲】</note><app n="1425050"><lem>修持</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">受持身</rdg></app>。心
<lb n="1425b26"/>常<note n="1425051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">求＝口【甲】</note><app n="1425051"><lem>求</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">口</rdg></app>誦此經。能滅生死苦。消伏於<app><lem></lem><rdg wit="【大】">於</rdg></app>毒害。
<lb n="1425b27"/><note n="1425052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">那摩＝南無【甲】</note><app n="1425052"><lem>那摩</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">南無</rdg></app>大明觀世音。觀明觀世音。高明觀世
<lb n="1425b28"/>音。開明觀世音。藥王菩薩。藥上菩薩。文殊
<lb n="1425b29"/><note n="1425053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔師利〕－【甲】</note><app n="1425053"><lem>師利</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>菩薩。普賢菩薩。虛空藏菩薩。地藏菩
<lb n="1425b30"/>薩。清涼<note n="1425054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">寶山億＝山臺【甲】</note><app n="1425054"><lem>寶山億</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">山臺</rdg></app>萬菩薩。<note n="1425055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">普＝寶【甲】</note><app n="1425055"><lem>普</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">寶</rdg></app>光如來<note n="1425056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">化＝花【甲】</note><app n="1425056"><lem>化</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">花</rdg></app>勝
<pb ed="T" id="T85.2898.1425c" n="1425c"/>
<lb n="1425c01"/>菩薩。念念誦此<note n="1425057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">偈＝經【甲】</note><app n="1425057"><lem>偈</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">經</rdg></app>。七佛世尊。即說&CB00057;曰</p><p type="idharani">離
<lb n="1425c02"/>波離波帝。求訶求訶帝。陀羅尼帝。尼訶羅
<lb n="1425c03"/>帝。毘<note n="1425058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">離尼＝尼摩離【甲】</note><app n="1425058"><lem>離尼</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">尼摩離</rdg></app>帝。摩訶迦帝。真<note n="1425059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">靈虔＝寧羯【甲】</note><app n="1425059"><lem>靈虔</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">寧羯</rdg></app>帝。<note n="1425060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">娑婆＝沙波【甲】</note><app n="1425060"><lem>娑婆</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">沙波</rdg></app>
<lb n="1425c04"/>訶</p>
<lb n="1425c05"/><lg><l>十方觀世音</l><l>一切諸菩薩</l><l>誓願救眾生</l>
<lb n="1425c06"/><l>稱名悉解脫</l><l>若有<note n="1425061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">智慧＝薄福【甲】</note><app n="1425061"><lem>智慧</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">薄福</rdg></app>者</l><l>慇懃為解脫</l>
<lb n="1425c07"/><l>但是有因緣</l><l>讀誦口不綴</l><l>誦經滿千遍</l>
<lb n="1425c08"/><l>念念心不絕</l><l>火焰不能傷</l><l>刀兵立摧折</l>
<lb n="1425c09"/><l>恚怒生歡喜</l><l>死者變成活</l><l>莫言此是虛</l>
<lb n="1425c10"/><l>諸佛不妄說</l></lg>
<lb n="1425c11"/><p><note n="1425062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說…經〕八字－【甲】</note><app n="1425062" word-count="8"><lem>佛說高王觀世音經</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="1425c12"/><lg><l>高王觀世音</l><l>能救諸苦<note n="1425063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">危＝厄【甲】</note><app n="1425063"><lem>危</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">厄</rdg></app></l><l>臨危急難中</l>
<lb n="1425c13"/><l><note n="1425064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（死者變成活））＝（（諸事得解脫拜念八菩薩））【甲】</note><app n="1425064"><lem>死者變成活</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">諸事得解脫拜念八菩薩</rdg></app></l><note n="1425065" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（諸佛…者））二十五＝（（持誦滿千遍薄福不信者重罪皆消滅諸佛語不虛是故虛是故應頂禮薄福不誦者））三十字【甲】</note><app n="1425065" word-count="25"><lem><l>諸佛語不虛</l><l>是故應頂禮</l>
<lb n="1425c14"/><l>持誦滿千遍</l><l>重罪皆消滅</l><l>薄福不信者</l></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">持誦滿千遍薄福不信者重罪皆消滅諸佛語不虛是故虛是故應頂禮薄福不誦者</rdg></app>
<lb n="1425c15"/><l>專<note n="1425066" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">貢＝負【甲】</note><app n="1425066"><lem>貢</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">負</rdg></app>受持經</l></lg>
<lb n="1425c16"/><p rend="margin-left:1"><note n="1425067" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔念〕－【甲】</note><app n="1425067"><lem>念</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>八大菩薩名號</p>
<lb n="1425c17"/><p>南無觀世音菩薩摩訶薩。南無彌勒菩薩摩
<lb n="1425c18"/>訶薩。南無虛空藏菩薩摩訶薩。南無普賢菩
<lb n="1425c19"/>薩</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T85.2898.1426a" n="1426a"/>
<lb n="1426a01"/><p>摩訶薩。<note n="1426001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（南無…消滅））六十九字＝（（南無地藏菩薩南無消災障菩薩南無妙吉祥金剛手菩薩摩訶薩））二十六字【甲】</note><note n="1426001" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="a"/>（（南無…消滅））六十九字＝（（南無地藏菩薩南無消災障菩薩南無妙吉祥金剛手菩薩摩訶薩））二十六字【甲】</note>南無金剛手菩薩摩訶薩。南無妙吉
<lb n="1426a02"/>祥菩薩摩訶薩。南無除蓋障菩薩摩訶薩。南
<lb n="1426a03"/>無地藏王菩薩摩訶薩。南無諸尊菩薩摩訶
<lb n="1426a04"/>薩</p>
<lb n="1426a05"/><lg><l>願以此功德</l><l>普及於一切</l>
<lb n="1426a06"/><l>誦滿一千遍</l><l>重罪皆消滅</l></lg>
<lb n="1426a07"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead><note n="1426002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（佛說…音））七字＝（（高王））二字【甲】</note><app n="1426002" word-count="7"><lem>佛說高王觀世音</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">高王</rdg></app>經<note place="inline">終</note></jhead></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>
